(b)  in relation to byelaws made by virtue of any provision of Chapter IV of Part III of this Act, means the Secretary of State or the Minister; and
(c)  in relation to any other byelaws, means the Secretary of State.    (2)  In this Schedule "relevant body" means the Authority or any water undertaker or sewerage undertaker.

